<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="theory-n">theory <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'θɪəri/    美 /'θɪri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 学说：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Darwin’s <strong>theory of</strong> evolution
达尔文的进化论</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 理论；原理：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>combine theory with practice
把理论和实践相结合</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 推测：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have this theory that most people prefer being at work to being at home.
依我看，大多数人喜欢工作而不愿意呆在家里。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-theory">in theory</h3>
<p>1.<strong>理论上：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It sounds fine in theory, but will it work?
理论上讲这是不错，但能否行得通?</p></div></div>